{"tid":755081,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬天才歡迎巴塞截胡天才：我們兄弟統治世界！","createTime":"2018-07-25T02:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T02:38:19.000Z","uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0c459206105c107a97c1155bb4bf946a1fd82413","tid":755081,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:07:15.000Z","msg":"巴塞最終截胡成功，以總價4200萬歐元簽下波圖前鋒馬高姆。他也收到了來自皇馬球員的祝福，那就是皇馬天才雲尼斯奧斯。兩人都是巴西球壇湧現出來的新星。<br />\n<br />\n　　此前，馬高姆一度接近加盟羅馬，波圖以及羅馬都進行了官方宣佈他將接受體檢，但是經過了24小時之後，巴塞最終截胡成功，以4200萬歐元的價格簽下了馬高姆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　在馬高姆的instagram下面，雲尼斯奧斯留言說：「恭喜你，兄弟！我們兄弟正在統治世界！上帝保佑！」"},{"pid":"badd437620a86d1ed15835ba21b23a526a4c24b3","tid":755081,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:10:02.000Z","msg":"雲尼斯奧斯 邊撚個黎"},{"pid":"4147f06a7a3032df4018d41791ceb19af05c1872","tid":755081,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"badd437620a86d1ed15835ba21b23a526a4c24b3","tid":755081,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:10:02.000Z","msg":"雲尼斯奧斯 邊撚個黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:11:29.000Z","msg":"力架"},{"pid":"ac8eb89a992e072ea3ad5eac3ad9b10a8f843601","tid":755081,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:11:48.000Z","msg":"之後兩個都俾人賣走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc94d843310c8c3f55ebcc33cc81d41ac3f61a1","tid":755081,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4147f06a7a3032df4018d41791ceb19af05c1872","tid":755081,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"badd437620a86d1ed15835ba21b23a526a4c24b3","tid":755081,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:10:02.000Z","msg":"雲尼斯奧斯 邊撚個黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:11:29.000Z","msg":"力架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:23:23.000Z","msg":"新羅賓奴"},{"pid":"c380527c2b443c1905c04cf2bc7451b485c3a543","tid":755081,"uid":82929,"lik